This assignments implements pokemon battling as well as an inventory system. There is an inventory where you are able to see your items such as Pokeball, potions, and revives which can also be refreshed at the Pokemart. You can also see your Pokemon party. Press B to open the inventory. In battle, you are able to use items for your Pokemon. Potion heals, revive revives, and Pokeball's can be used to capture wild Pokemon. In trainer battle's you can also switch Pokemon. When all your Pokemon's hp reach 0, it is game over. If your Pokemon are hurt, they can be healed at the Pokemon Center.
